    {"type":"text","x":66,"y":760,"width":1240,"height":120,"text":"Recovery path: startup scans non-terminal executions, expired leases are requeued, and only missing or uncommitted checkpoints are retried. That is the durable-execution guarantee in one diagram.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","fontColor":"#334155"}
